      "description": "Great opportunity to own a solid, dependable vehicle! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and it shows. The exterior presents nicely with only the minor blemishes you'd expect from regular use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it's running well and ready for the road. Not a showroom queen, but a reliable, attractive car that offers real value for the price. Come take a look \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
