    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains a deep, glossy finish free of scratches, chips, or dents. All body panels are straight and properly aligned, and the glass is clear and undamaged throughout. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells nearly new \u2014 seats show no wear, the dashboard and trim are pristine, and all electronics, controls, and comfort features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with strong, confident power delivery. Service records are available and reflect consistent, proper maintenance. Tires have excellent tread remaining, brakes are in great shape, and the suspension feels tight and responsive. This is a turn-key vehicle requiring absolutely nothing before driving \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic fixes, no surprises. If you're looking for a used car that genuinely feels like new, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
